# Keep Vercel uploads small: it builds from source on its own servers, so none
# of this needs to be sent. .worktrees (a second checkout + its node_modules) and
# the gitignored 229 MB public/bg/space.mp4 are what blew past the 100 MB limit.
.git
node_modules
.worktrees
dist
.vercel
public/bg
*.mp4
*.mov
# ...but DO ship the one Star Wars menu background video (24 MB, well under limits).
!public/starwars/sith-trooper.mp4
